Confirm                 Prompts the user for confirmation in the
                        console
GetDirectory            prompts the user for a directory
GetMultiUserchoice      allows the user to select 1 or more of the
                        choices,
GetPresets              Returns the preset input
GetUserChoice           Prompts the user to choose one of the given set
                        of choices
Preset                  sets the preset input global variable, which if
                        not empty will be used instead of .ReadLine.
ReadInt                 Reads an int input from the user and re-prompts
                        if they didn't enter an int
